        "markdown": "# Glue Job Monitoring Dashboard\nThis dashboard replicates the AWS Glue console Monitoring page. **Custom Widget** panels require deploying the companion Lambda function (`glueJobMonitorWidget`). See the README for setup instructions.\n\n---"
